Subject: [PATCH v6 09/14] riscv: Fix accessing pfn bits in PTEs for non-32bit variants
Date:   Wed,  9 Feb 2022 13:37:55 +0100
Message-Id: <20220209123800.269774-10-heiko@sntech.de>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.2
